arStrings.szText: Your {c_important}Golem{/c} Active also causes your Golem to erupt, dealing {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} Physical damage to surrounding enemies. Your Golem consumes Corpses to reduce its remaining Cooldown by {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} second.
